org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.as

Interface IFileNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASNode, IScopedNode, ISourceLocation
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IMXMLFileNode, IOldMXMLFileNode, IResourceBundleFileNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileNode, FXGFileNode, MXMLFileNode, ResourceBundleFileNode

    public interface IFileNode
extends IScopedNode
    An AST node representing an ActionScript file being compiled.

    An IFileNode is the root of the AST (abstract syntax tree) produced for a file.

    If the file includes other files, a single IFileNode is produced.

    The shape of this node is 

     IFileNode
   IASNode <-- getChild(0)
   IASNode <-- getChild(1)
   ...
